videos.headline: Perine takes off for 61-yard score
videos.description: Lamical Perine runs up the middle of the field untouched as Florida scores just 40 seconds into the game vs. No. 24 Virginia.

videos.headline: Ridiculous Virginia interception leads to TD on next play
videos.description: After Virginia's Nick Grant intercepts Kyle Trask's pass, Bryce Perkins finds Terrell Jana on the very next play for a Cavaliers touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ridiculous Virginia interception leads to TD on next play) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Perine scores 2nd TD of first quarter
videos.description: Lamical Perine grabs the pass from Kyle Trask and turns on the jets all the way to a 16-yard touchdown, Perine's second of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Perine scores 2nd TD of first quarter) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Dubois mosses defender for TD
videos.description: Virginia's Bryce Perkins scrambles to avoid the sack and finds Hasise Dubois who makes an incredible catch in the back of the end zone.

videos.headline: Perine turns on jets for TD
videos.description: Lamical Perine records his third touchdown of the first half off of a 10-yard rush in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Perine turns on jets for TD) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Reed scores off Virginia screen pass
videos.description: Joe Reed scores the touchdown off a Virginia screen pass to pull within one possession of Florida.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Reed scores off Virginia screen pass) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Trask calls his own number for TD
videos.description: Kyle Trask keeps the ball himself and rushes into the end zone for a Gators touchdown in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Trask calls his own number for TD) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Perine's trio of TDs power Gators to Orange Bowl win
videos.description: Lamical Perine goes off for 138 rushing yards and three total touchdowns as the Gators take care of business in the Capital One Orange Bowl and defeat Virginia 36-28.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Perine’s trio of TDs power Gators to Orange Bowl win) 2019/12/30 ESHEET SOTFULL
